86KS@u:Pv#y}|=%KgXJu.text: Welcome to my first ever project, old FNaF 1 Plus! I think it's safe enough to say that this is very accurate and similar to the real game, but fanmade things have been added by me.  In this game you will find a night 8, cheats, endless mode, 5/20 mode, and more! Take a look around my sprites and code as much as you want, you could tell I was a beginner to the mechanics of coding on scratch! lots of "if then - else" gaps lol.  You can even filter around with the code to have a little bit of extra fun with this game, it won't change anything promise! good luck :)
